# Default: ignore everything in this directory (Schemathesis writes JUnit /
# HAR / NDJSON reports here at runtime; the dir is also chmod 0777 to let the
# docker container's UID write). The exceptions below preserve the deterministic
# case runner + coverage gate (TRA-692).
*
!.gitignore
!explicit_error_cases.py
!check_field_error_coverage.py
!test_check_field_error_coverage.py
!requirements.txt
